course_title: Intermediate Classical and Quranic Arabic II

sections.comments: Please check cnrs.ubc.ca or contact the instructor for web-based course delivery information. Students who have received credit for ARBC 400 may not also receive credit for ARBC 201 or 202

description: Classical Arabic. Designed to further enrich vocabulary and grammar and to enhance fluency in reading and interpreting longer texts from Qur'an, Hadith and other genres.
